description: Strengthening the capacity of the National Institute of Statistics to increase the credibility of the census data and the legitimacy particularly regarding national minorities’ issues.

subproject.description: To increase the 2011 population census legitimacy and credibility/coverage in terms of the inclusiveness primarily of national minorities and Roma groups and incidentally of other under-represented and vulnerable groups and groups at risk, including refugees.
